  <brief_title>The Correlation Between Genetic Polymorphism, Platelet Activity, Clopidogrel Responsiveness, and Serum Adipokine Concentration in Asian Acute Coronary Syndrome Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Correlation Between Genetic Polymorphism, Platelet Activity, , Clopidogrel Responsiveness, and Serum Adipokine Concentration in Asian Acute Coronary Syndrome Patients</official_title>
