  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this study, we evaluate the acute coronary syndrome patients to see if there is
      correlation between platelet activity, genetic polymorphism (CYP2C19 and ABCB1), serum
      adipokines level, and Clopidogrel responsiveness.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
